{
  "stem": "18056.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 244.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Harry Guterman, G-U-T-E-R-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Harry is H-A-R-R-Y.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Herszel, Hersz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "H-E-R-S-Z.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Guterman, G-U-T-E-R-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But sometimes a different language, some people would call-- they couldn't-- they couldn't pronounce the name Hersz or they couldn't pronounce so well Harry, so they would call me maybe a different name, but just nothing official.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born June 1925, the 13th of June.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My current age is 71 and 2 months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born in Konstantynow, near Lodz in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to spell Konstantynow, it's K-O-N-S-T-A-N-T-Y-N-O-W.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's name was Chaim, C-H-A-I-M, Guterman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- he was born around 1897, or '98, at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- he worked together with my grandfather in his business, also worked for himself in his business, in the textile industry.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after-- in 1930s, when Hitler came to power in Germany, in Poland the anti-Semitism became very active and dangerous for a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody was looking a way how to get out of Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the first thing they were thinking about at the time was Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Zionistic movement started out at that time, to go to Palestine and maybe build a country there, and a new home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So being that he was the oldest child, the oldest son in the family, it was pretty much decided that he should be the one to go to Palestine and to see how it is going to be there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so when he arrived there, he liked it and he never wanted to come back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the whole thing was that we were working on-- on the premises and the idea to pack up in Poland and go to Palestine at that time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, the war broke out in 1939.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
